Nadia Buari, one of the most popular Ghanaian actresses in Nollywood, has revealed fellow superstar film maker, Van Vicker as the father of her four daughters. Buari made the revelation in a video she posted on Instagram on Monday, where she showed off Vicker as the father of her beautiful daughters. She was spotted with Vicker as she unveiled him as the father of her kids, saying, “so, a lot of you have been asking me to reveal the identity of the father of my kids. “Today, I have a surprise for you. Yes you guessed right. I want to reveal to you the man who gave me four adorable queens.” Responding in the video, Vicker said, “Hello Everybody! I’m feeling myself.” Buari, who is a popular Ghanaian actress, movie producer and businesswoman, was married to a Lebanese man whose name is not known.